<!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:red;">Priest:</span><!--EZCODE FONT END-->  Let us give thanks to the Lord, our God.   <!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:red;">All:</span><!--EZCODE FONT END-->  <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>It is right to give him thanks and praise.</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
