<!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:red;">Priest:</span><!--EZCODE FONT END-->  Lord, you are holy indeed, the fountain of all holiness. Let your Spirit come upon these gifts to make them holy, so that they may become for us the body and blood of our Lord, Jesus Christ. <br>
