When the supper was ended, he took the cup. Again he gave you thanks and praise, gave the cup to his disciples, and said: <br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Take this, all of you, and drink from it; this is the cup of my blood, the blood of the new and everlasting covenant. It will be shed for you and for all so that sins may be forgiven. Do this in memory of me.</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> <br>
