<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Great Amen:</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:red;">Priest:</span><!--EZCODE FONT END-->  Through him, with him, and in him, in the unity of the Holy Spirit,<br>
