<br>
<!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:red;">Priest:</span><!--EZCODE FONT END-->  Deliver us, Lord, from every evil, and grant us peace in our day. In your mercy keep us free from sin and protect us from all anxiety as we wait in joyful hope for the coming of our Savior, Jesus Christ.<br>
